{{distinguish|Interculturalism}}
'''Intraculturalism''' is the study of behavior within one [[cultural group]]. For example, [[Value (personal and social)|value]] variations among Palestinians are intracultural. This is often part of [[Subaltern Studies]], [[development studies]] and [[sociology]].

